summary: Degeneracy Meets Artificial Intelligence - DegenAI is a full suite of Telegram-based and AI-backed utilities for the common trader. With our flagship product, Pennyworth, users can buy, sell, bridge, snipe, copytrade on DEX’s and much more while also being able to link your CEX account and leverage trade CEX coins! DegenAI stakers are rewarded shares of the Degen Protocol revenue via The Engine. For more information regarding the project, please refer to our Medium blog posts.
